                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18221204-50-off269 t18221204-50-crimeloc272"></join>. We had a stand of things outside by the window. On the 30th of October, I was at the door, and received information, and laid hold of<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182212040020"></xptr>the prisoner with some plates under her cloak - she knelt down and put them on the curb stone. Phillips took them up, and I took her. I know them by the pattern.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18221204-50-person442">
                  BARNARD 
                  PHILLIPS
               <interp inst="t18221204-50-person442" type="surname" value="PHILLIPS"></interp>
