                     <interp inst="t18221204-50-person442" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I have a stand by Mr. Carter's On the 30th of October, I saw the prisoner take some plates of the bottom of the shop window; she crossed over, and was going down Princes-street. I told Alley, and saw him stop her. She put them on the ground about twenty yards off.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. It was mere distress. I had a child dead at the time.</p>
               <p>
